parameters: \n<Imp>Hey, hey! I told you not to come back... Why did you come...

\n<Imp>What? You came to exterminate me? After all that's happened,
now you want to exterminate me? Hah... Fine, fine. Just kill
me quickly, will you?

\n<Imp>Huh? That's not it? You just came to see me...? Huh? That
makes no sense...

\n<Imp>Ahh, I get it. My pussy felt so good that you wanted to do
it again. You should've just said that from the start.

\n<Imp>You know, I could kill you anytime if I wanted to, right? Do
you really think you can win at level 1?

\n<Imp>Go home before I change my mind. Seriously, I'll kill you.
Leave.

\n<Imp>Ah, that stuff over there? I killed a merchant and stole it.
If there's anything you want, feel free to take it.

\n<Imp>(Even though they're stronger than me... I really can't
figure out what they're thinking. Are they mocking me...?)

\n<Imp>Imps are incredibly numerous, right? Like orcs, we're a
species specialized in breeding. But that also means we're
not that strong.

\n<Imp>Still, we have enough power to kill an amateur who's armed
with a weapon.

\n<Imp>I don't know why, but lately, it seems the Demon Lord has
been experimenting with "turning existing monsters into
succubi."

\n<Imp>I used to be a regular monster until a little while ago.
This body is more convenient for various reasons. I like it.

\n<Imp>Hey, you're an idiot, so you probably came back because you
want to do lewd things with me again, right? Fine. Let's get
it over with quickly.

\n<Imp>I've drained so much magical power from humans that I've
become a higher-ranking imp. Well, I just call myself that.

\n<Imp>You know I'm a despicable monster who's killed lots of
people, and yet you still want to do lewd things with me.
You're pretty low yourself.

\n<Imp>What's wrong? Getting horny? It looks like that thing of
yours is getting bigger. Hey, why is that? Is my body that
erotic?

\n<Imp>I told you I'd kill you if you came back, right? Do you
understand what will happen if we do lewd things? Teehee♥

\n<Imp>Sigh... Alright, alright. You want to do it, don't you? Just
do what you need to do and then leave quickly.
\n<Imp>So? What do you want me to do to you?\C[14]（Imp Lv\v[706]）

\n<Imp>Taking the goods that monsters stole from merchants for
yourself... What kind of adventurer does that?

\n<Imp>Ahh, if you steal that, you'll become a criminal too. Go
ahead, take it. Kukuku♥

\n<Imp>Ah... that's right. I've left something you might like over
there. Feel free to take it.

\n<Imp>That's something I stole from the merchants. You can take
it, but you'll be an accomplice too♥ Hehehe♥
